execute from Android Studio Terminal (to make debug apk):

./gradlew assembleDebug

Go to Android SDK -> Platform Tools (manually) OR

cd $HOME/Android/Sdk/platform-tools/

execute :

./adb install -r /home/fab/do-android/app/build/outputs/apk/app-debug.apk


./adb install -r /home/fab/TrueWheels/app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk

OR

./adb shell //open adb shell
su //get root permissions
pm uninstall your.package.name //uninstall the app

./adb install /home/fab/do-android/app/build/outputs/apk/app-debug.apk

